        {
          "field_name": "eligibility_text",
          "candidate_value": "How does contactless payment work? TD Business Credit Cards with chip & PIN technology can wirelessly connect with a secure reader on a merchant's point-of-sale terminal. It\u2019s simple and quick: Depending on the terminal, either wave or tap your TD Business Credit Card in front of",
