        {
          "field_name": "fee_waiver_condition",
          "candidate_value": "General information about fees Monthly fees For some of our accounts, you'll pay a monthly fee, no matter how much or how little you use the account. Monthly fees are calculated based on the type of account you hold on the last day of the month. However, for some of our accounts ",
